+	/* Hugepage cannot be protected, so nothing to do */
+	if (PageHuge(page))
+		return 0;
+
+	/*
+	 * PG_arch_1 is used in 3 places:
+	 * 1. for kernel page tables during early boot
+	 * 2. for storage keys of huge pages and KVM
